text: I am deeply grateful for the opportunity to have served as the 78th Secretary of the @USTreasury. It has been one of the greatest honors of my career to work alongside such dedicated public servants who paired intellectual rigor with moral purpose. https://t.co/0FHO4fu0Sb

name: Secretary Janet Yellen (Archived)
text: We face great challenges as a country right now. To recover, we must restore the American dream‚Äîa society where each person can rise to their potential and dream even bigger for their children. As Treasury Secretary, I will work every day towards rebuilding that dream for all.

name: Secretary Janet Yellen (Archived)
text: Economics isn‚Äôt just something you find in a textbook. It can be a potent tool to right past wrongs and improve people‚Äôs lives. That‚Äôs why so many of Treasury‚Äôs 84,000 public servants joined the Department. Today, I am proud to be one of them.

name: Secretary Janet Yellen (Archived)
text: Thank you @HamiltonMusical for including me in your narrative. I promise to bring Alexander‚Äôs (non-stop) work ethic to the room where it happens.

name: Secretary Janet Yellen (Archived)
text: The Treasury Department must be an institution that wakes up every morning thinking about the American people. Your jobs, your paychecks. Your struggles, your hopes. Your dignity. And your limitless potential. We will work to restore that public trust and promise. https://t.co/ubxrE0sIc6

name: Secretary Janet Yellen (Archived)
text: The President is absolutely right: The benefits of acting now ‚Äî and acting big ‚Äî will far outweigh the costs in the long run.

name: Secretary Janet Yellen (Archived)
text: I just received a demo of the upcoming IRS Direct File tool. The IRS has built an impressive product that will give taxpayers a secure option to file their taxes online for free. This pilot program will start small in 2024, to allow the IRS to test it and learn from taxpayers. https://t.co/1BvmMCcEdD
